;(If {{F|FSV_CerydraTalkOrder}} is undefined 1)
::'''Cerydra:''' Customer numbers have been on a sugar high lately, proving our sweet-themed strategy was exactly the right flavor. Of course, now Dux Fatorum has to juggle many more items on their daily menu.
;(Otherwise, if {{F|FSV_CerydraTalkOrder}} is undefined 2)
::'''Cerydra:''' The "Chef Showdown" has really stirred the pot of public interest, and that white-haired chef has been cooking up a storm in practice. Looks like we're in for quite the culinary battle.
;(Otherwise, if {{F|FSV_CerydraTalkOrder}} is undefined 3)
::'''Cerydra:''' Despite the Kremnoan Chef's obvious confidence, he never turns down the heat on his training. I must admit, even I'm hungry to see who will win.
;(Otherwise, if {{F|FSV_CerydraTalkOrder}} is undefined 4)
::'''Cerydra:''' I've never seen such extraordinary giant fruits before. The scholar appears satisfied with the current results and is working faster on new varieties. Hopefully without another fruitful disaster.
;(Otherwise, if {{F|FSV_CerydraTalkOrder}} is undefined 5)
::'''Cerydra:''' Promotions may help burn through stock fast, but how do we attract more customers? That is up to Dux Celeripes' talent.
;(Otherwise)
::'''Cerydra:''' Running a restaurant is no different from governing a city-state. Every move must be cautiously considered. Manager, are you ready to open for business?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_803510631_91-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_803510631_91-->
