:::{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to review our restaurant event with you.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163130-->
::::'''Cerydra:''' Heh. I'll admit, launching a restaurant event is indeed a good move. It brings in traffic and gives each department head a chance to shine. Smart decision, manager.
::::'''Cerydra:''' What exactly do you want to talk about?
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_fupan-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_fupan-->
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Sweetie Festival...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163133-->
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Dux Fatorum can barely reach the top of the kitchen pot, yet she's a natural at hospitality. Truly impressive.
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Running a restaurant means you can't please everyone, so choosing sweets as the first theme is definitely a smart call. It works perfectly with our current ingredient stock while delivering maximum customer satisfaction.
:::::'''Cerydra:''' As for the sweetest dish... Heh, I'm pretty sure they already know the answer in their hearts.
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Chef Showdown...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163137-->
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Hahaha! Who'd have thought a duel between our two chefs would stir up such a commotion in the fairies' domain?
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Good thing Dux Gladiorum showed up just in time to stop things from spiraling further. The two chefs' skills are truly top-tier, no doubt. But pleasing the demigod of Ocean is no easy feat. At least, I've never seen it done myself.
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Still, the restaurant made quite a splash in the Maze. That's worth celebrating.
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Harvest Festival...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163141-->
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Who would've thought that scholar could actually grow crops that massive? The kitchen won't have to worry about running out of ingredients anytime soon.
:::::'''Cerydra:''' As for the surplus... plenty of ways to put it to use. Better that than starving with empty pots.
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Great Sale...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163144-->
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Value for money is always the ultimate pursuit. It's human nature, and fairies are no exception.
:::::'''Cerydra:''' Dux Celeripes sure has an eye for what customers really want. And... heh, by pocketing that coin, she showed she knows exactly what she values too.
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Exit}} Let's catch up another time!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163124-->
::::'''Cerydra:''' No trouble at all. I'll be here.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
